# Summary
Convizit is an AI-based Digital Experience Data Platform that automatically captures website user behavior and sends structured, named, and enriched events to Amplitude approximately every 30 minutes, with events identified by "source": "Convizit" in the JSON payload and including detailed user interaction data.

